{"tid":607321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：鋼鐵的真相。中國出口美國的鋼和鋁，因為品質差，數量其實不多，根據日本的統計，只是佔美國入口的3%左右。","createTime":"2018-03-27T08:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T12:46:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad4f0efeca93bbef1ad442968c2770e7a48aba7","tid":607321,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T08:06:23.000Z","msg":"陳雲：鋼鐵的真相。中國出口美國的鋼和鋁，因為品質差，數量其實不多，根據日本的統計，只是佔美國入口的3%左右。反而中國出口好多品質一般的鋼和鋁去台灣及東南亞國家的廠房，製造廉價工業品，之後輸出美國。現在美國的做法，是追踪中國鋼鋁原料，如果發現有盟友採用中國鋼鋁原料，就會徵收關稅。目前台灣正在被考核的名單之中。<br />\n這是好毒辣的方法，因為會打擊中國鋼鐵原料的全球出口，趕走中國原料的買家，令到中國境內聘請大批工人的煉鐵廠、回收廠倒閉，產生失業。"},{"pid":"ba94bd082fd1606638c2bec243c4b5e80c7a95f6","tid":607321,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551e053973f2dfe55724ca5d255c3c1bfd2515b4","tid":607321,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f913ea3a5116fce08dc9b8c8c29c46f227562ae9","tid":607321,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:25:28.000Z","msg":"買過中國同美國啲6061鋁合金，中國嗰啲好似加咗太多silicon，鋸下就睇得出分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408cde6eb54c5e498e89a9ec6aac80ddd554258a","tid":607321,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f913ea3a5116fce08dc9b8c8c29c46f227562ae9","tid":607321,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:25:28.000Z","msg":"買過中國同美國啲6061鋁合金，中國嗰啲好似加咗太多silicon，鋸下就睇得出分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:39:19.000Z","msg":"6061 T幾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d612454dadfa9bad84780462477e8ba37fc8dfaa","tid":607321,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"